- [BankingException.java](src/main/java/com/challenge/banking/BankingException.java) - Changed inheritance from Exception to RuntimeException

## Technical Details
The change was minimal but crucial:
```java
// Before (causing compilation error)
public class BankingException extends Exception

// After (fixed)
public class BankingException extends RuntimeException
```

